data.description: Welcome to this charming house in the desirable Jerilyn Gerrell Subdivision, located in the heart of Cleveland. The house is spread over a generous 1282 sq ft and offers an abundance of natural light throughout. Inside, you'll find three spacious bedrooms, each with ceiling fans and either wooden or tiled floors. The master bedroom features an ensuite bathroom for added convenience. The second bathroom is easily accessible from the other bedrooms. The kitchen is a chef's dream, complete with a double fridge and a ceiling fan to keep you cool while you cook. The wooden floors add a touch of warmth and character to the space. Step outside onto the deck and take in the countryside views. This is the perfect spot to relax and enjoy nature's beauty. The location of this house is truly unbeatable. Situated in Cleveland, you'll have easy access to all the amenities the area has to offer, including shops, restaurants, and schools. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your new home. Contact us today to schedule a showing and see all that this wonderful property has to offer.
